Detailed Description

template<typename T, Integer _lo = 0, Integer _hi = -1>
class Step::List< T, _lo, _hi >

C++ implementation of EXPRESS container 'LIST' see http://tools.openoffice.org/performance/aggregate_classes.html we are using STL vectors instead of lists to favorise sequential access.
